<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6673462>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25–31. Pogonostoma (Microstenocera) andreevae Moravec, type locality Ranomafana. 25—pronotum, ♀ (CJVB); 26–27—labrum: 26—♀, HT (JWCW, later in ZSM) 27—♀ (CJVB); 28—metatarsus, ♀ (CJVB); 29—male aedeagus, AT (CAS); 30—habitus, ♂, 7.5 mm,AT (CAS); 31—ditto, partial ventral view on testaceous metatarsi. Bars = 1 mm (30–31—im- age credit Rachel Diaz-Bastin, CAS)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6673462/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6673458>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–10. Pogonostoma (Microstenocera) borisbubeniki sp. nov.,Ambohitantely.1—habitus, ♂, 8.6 mm, HT (NMPC); 2—head, ♀, AT (CJVB); 3—antennomeres 1–6, ♀, AT; 4—mandibles, ♂, HT; 5—lacinia and galea, ♂, HT; 6–10—labrum: 6—♂, HT; 7—♂, PT (CCJM); 8—♀, AT; 9—♀, PT (CCJM); 10—♀, PT (CMTD). Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6673458/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6673460>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–24. Pogonostoma (Microstenocera) borisbubeniki sp. nov., Ambohitantely. 11–12—pronotum: 11—♂, HT (NMPC); 12—♀, AT (CJVB); 13–14—elytron: 13—♂, PT (CCJM); 14—♀, AT; 15–16—elytral apex: 15—♂, HT; 16—♀, AT; 17–24—male aedeagus or its apex: 17—HT; 18—PT (CMTD); 19—PT (COSJ); 20—PT (BBFM); 21—PT (CCJM); 22— (without parameres) PT (BMNH); 23—PT (CCJM); 24—ditto, dorsal view. Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6673460/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6673470>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34–35. Pogonostoma (Microstenocera) borisbubeniki sp. nov., Ambohitantely Special Reserve. 34—collecting site; 35—unregulated spread of an invasive grass species within the reserve." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6673470/files/figure.png" ;
